## Implementation Plan: Generalizing the Action Model (Roadmap Item 3)

### Summary of Changes

Three files require edits. Two files are structural changes to types and executors. The test file requires mechanical additions at four manually-constructed action object sites. No logic is altered anywhere — this is purely additive and structural.

