**Why this file needs updating:** The test file constructs four `DeployAction` object literals directly (not via `planDeploy`). Because `SkillDirDeployAction` requires `kind: "skill-dir"`, TypeScript will report an error at each of those four construction sites. Each requires adding one line: `kind: "skill-dir"`.

