The edits must be applied in this order to avoid intermediate type errors during implementation:

1. `src/types.ts` — establishes the new interface names and `kind` discriminant
2. `src/core/deploy.ts` — `planDeploy` push, then `executeDeploy` switch
3. `src/core/revert.ts` — `planRevert` push, `planRevertAll` push, then `executeRevert` switch
4. `test/deploy.test.ts` — add `kind: "skill-dir"` to the four manual construction sites

